Pop Art Studio v3.0
Pop Art Studio is very easy to use graphics editing software. It supports BMP, JPG, GIF, PNG and TIFF formatted images.
Version 3.0 contains many Andy Warhol effects and the famous Roy Lichtenstein effect. All colors are now fully customizable. The program provides an endless selection of text and drawing tools, filters and color adjustment capabilities. The large clip art collection is ideal for your design and creation of logo&#039;s. The Template Library provides many useful examples of logo&#039;s and vector designs
